title: [Four Winds Sergeant's Office]
[Mist Harbor Sergeant's Office]
description: The entry area of the law of the Isle of the Four Winds has the desk of the First Sergeant pushed against the wall.  A pile of ropes and shackles spills out of an overflowing barrel near the exit, and several tripods of spears flank either side of the door to the jail.
